OL,3,C'It's appalling': Disabled people who
OL,4,Ccan walk refused hospital transport
OL,6,FStaff were told about the decision in
OL,7,Fan email that came from the funding
OL,8,Fbodies of Cheshire and Merseyside NHS.
OL,10,FJoanne said: "At first I was
OL,11,Fflabbergasted. I asked her to check
OL,12,Fand double check.
OL,14,F"I was scared because if I don't get
OL,15,Fthis looked after properly, I could
OL,16,Fdie."
OL,18,FShe added it would be impossible to
OL,19,Fget to the hospital on her own
OL,20,F"because I am totally blind".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
