OL,3,C'It's appalling': Disabled people who
OL,4,Ccan walk refused hospital transport
OL,6,F"It is impossible, to go out into the
OL,7,Foutside world just a long cane, I
OL,8,Fcan't do it becayse I can't tell where
OL,9,FI am," she said.
OL,11,F"I haven't got anyone who can take me.
OL,12,FAll the friends I've got here, they
OL,13,Fwork.
OL,15,F"My husband can't take me because he's
OL,16,Fregistered disabled himself."
OL,18,FShe added: "I think it's appalling. I
OL,19,Fget really upset because people think
OL,20,Fall disabled people have the same
OL,21,Fneeds."
