OL,3,C'It's appalling': Disabled people who
OL,4,Ccan walk refused hospital transport
OL,6,FPensioner Robin Crosby, who has
OL,7,Fnumerous conditions which means he
OL,8,Fneeds two sticks to walk, has also
OL,9,Flost his transport.
OL,11,FHe had to pay #40 out of his own
OL,12,Fpocket for a taxi to his last
OL,13,Fappointment.
OL,15,F"I'm 88-years-old, I've served my
OL,16,Fcountry and now I'm in lots of pain
OL,17,Fand I can't get help," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
