OL,3,C'It's appalling': Disabled people who
OL,4,Ccan walk refused hospital transport
OL,6,F"I find life is not easy for me any
OL,7,Fway, I can't go out, I sit in my chair
OL,8,F24 hours a day, I sleep in it because
OL,9,FI can't sleep in a bed because of my
OL,10,Fback.
OL,12,F"It just makes you despair really."
OL,14,FWMAS says it has had to prioritise who
OL,15,Fqualifies for the service as the trust
OL,16,Fwhich hired them - NHS Cheshire and
OL,17,FMerseyside Integrated Care Board (ICB)
OL,18,F- is not paying its bills.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
