OL,3,C'It's appalling': Disabled people who
OL,4,Ccan walk refused hospital transport
OL,6,FJustin Madders, Labour MP for
OL,7,FEllesmere Port and Bromborough, says
OL,8,Fhe is "furious" that vulnerable
OL,9,Fpatients have been abandoned without
OL,10,Fwarning.
OL,12,F"All we know is that people who were
OL,13,Fpreviously relying on patient
OL,14,Fambulance services are being told they
OL,15,Fare no longer eligible," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
