OL,3,C'It's appalling': Disabled people who
OL,4,Ccan walk refused hospital transport
OL,6,F"That means they're missing
OL,7,Fappointments, the ICB don't seem to be
OL,8,Fwanting to address the issue, and in
OL,9,Ffact seem to be pretending it's not
OL,10,Fhappening, but it is happening and it
OL,11,Fneeds addressing now."
