OL,3,C'It's appalling': Disabled people who
OL,4,Ccan walk refused hospital transport
OL,6,F"The Trust has been in discussion with
OL,7,Fthe ICB for many months trying to find
OL,8,Fa solution to the situation but
OL,9,Funfortunately, this has so far not
OL,10,Fbeen possible. Discussions are
OL,11,Fcontinuing on an almost daily basis."
OL,13,FNHS Cheshire and Merseyside ICB said
OL,14,Fhelp is available for patients who are
OL,15,Fstruggling for transport, but did not
OL,16,Faddress accusations it has not been
OL,17,Fpaying WMAS.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
