OL,3,C'It's appalling': Disabled people who
OL,4,Ccan walk refused hospital transport
OL,6,F"We are in ongoing discussions with
OL,7,FWest Midlands Ambulance Service and
OL,8,Fcontinue to fund the service in line
OL,9,Fwith the existing core contract," a
OL,10,Fspokesperson said.
OL,12,F"We are seeking and expect assurance
OL,13,Fthat all eligible patients continue to
OL,14,Fbe transported in line with the
OL,15,Fnational eligibility framework."
